OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion head coach sacked
OL,4,Cafter ten away defeats in a row
OL,6,FHead coach Ryan Mason has been sacked
OL,7,Fby West Bromwich Albion after the
OL,8,Fclub's defeat against Leicester City.
OL,10,FIt was the team's 10th away defeat in
OL,11,Fa row, losing 2-1 at the King Power
OL,12,FStadium.
OL,14,FThe loss left the Baggies 18th in the
OL,15,Ftable.
OL,17,FMason has been sacked seven months
OL,18,Finto his three-year contract, with
OL,19,Ffirst team coach James Morrison now
OL,20,Fstepping in on an interim basis.
