OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion head coach sacked
OL,4,Cafter ten away defeats in a row
OL,6,FThe club's assistant head coach Nigel
OL,7,FGibbs and head of performance Sam
OL,8,FPooley have also left.
OL,10,FThis is the second head coach sacking
OL,11,Fin nine months, after former coach
OL,12,FTony Mowbray was dismissed last April.
OL,14,FIn a statement, West Bromwich Albion
OL,15,Fsaid: "The club would like to place on
OL,16,Frecord its thanks to Ryan, Nigel and
OL,17,FSam for their efforts and wishes all
OL,18,Fthree the very best for the future."
